					<div class="fusion-post-content-container">
						<p> At present, there are more than 1000 kinds of dinosaurs known to man, which are all over every continent of the earth. On land, dinosaurs are worthy of being the overlord. What role did dinosaurs play in lakes and rivers? In the age of dinosaurs, there are many ancient creatures with the name of "dragon" in the ocean, such as plesiosaurs and ichthyosaurs, but they don't really belong to the dinosaur family. Scientists have not been able to find the remains of dinosaurs in the aquatic environment, some even think that dinosaurs as thermophilic animals can not survive in the <a href="https://www.dinosaurjoy.com/how-to-prove-that-dinosaurs-can-swim/">[...]</a></p>					</div>
